  "source": "// Demonstrates several built-in operations in sequence.\n// Computes a hash, generates a public key, commits a value\n// and combines the results.\nseiyaku Example {\n    kotoage fn complex(a, b) {\n        let c = a + b;\n        let d = poseidon2(c, b);\n        let e = pubkgen(d);\n        let f = valcom(e, a);\n        let g = f + d;\n    }\n}\n",
